---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
    <div>
        <figure class="relative">
            <img src="/images/banner.webp" alt="Main banner" class="w-full" />
            <h1 class="text-center font-parisienne absolute text-gray-800 top-1/2 left-2/3  -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-7xl">
                Terapia integral y personalizada para tus necesidades
            </h1>
        </figure>
        <section class="max-w-6xl px-4 py-8 mx-auto flex flex-col gap-20 bg-white">
            <article class="flex justify-between align-center gap-20">
                <figure class="-mt-20 relative max-w-xs shadow-xl self-start">
                    <img src="/images/abel-tall.webp" alt="Oscar Abel Mascareno Cervantes" class="w-full" />
                </figure>
                <div class=" [&_p]:mb-5 self-center">
                    <h2 class="mb-4 text-center ">
                        You Don’t Have to Find Your Way Alone.
                    </h2>
                    <p>
                        If you’ve been feeling stressed, anxious, depressed; experiencing poor sleep, self-doubt, isolation; having difficulty in relationships, or are finally ready to dig into your childhood trauma, I’m here to help you sort it out. 
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Together we’ll navigate different ways of looking at and working through your struggles while also exploring how you got there to begin with.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </article>
            
            <article class="flex justify-between [&_div]:mt-5">
                <div class="max-w-xl">
                    <h2 class="mb-4 text-center"> Working with me looks like</h2>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="mb-4 font-arimo"> Solution-Focused </h3>
                        <p class="">
                            Let’s set your sights on the future you—the person you want to
                            be when you wake up every morning. I’ll help you set
                            achievable, feel-good goals that focus on solutions rather than
                            just the problems.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="mb-4"> Person-Centered </h3>
                        <p>
                            I want to help you uncover your inner strengths, gain new
                            insights, and hone the skills you need in order to overcome
                            life’s challenges. I hold a judgement-free space reserved for
                            your deepest, most personal growth.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <figure class="max-w-xs shadow-xl self-start translate-y-20">
                    <img src="/images/mountain.webp" alt="Mountain" class="w-full" />
                </figure>
            </article>
        </section>
        <section class="
            mt-20 h-100 
            flex justify-center text-white
            items-center font-arimo overflow-y-scroll
            bg-[url('/images/paralax.webp')] 
            font-
            bg-cover  bg-fixed bg-center bg-no-repeat"
        >
            <article class="max-w-6xl px-4 py-8 text-4xl mx-auto flex flex-col gap-10 text-center">
                "Hay sabiduría en el trauma: cuando nos damos cuenta de que nuestras respuestas e impresiones traumáticas no somos nosotros mismos, y que podemos superarlas y así convertirnos en nuestro verdadero yo."
                <span class="text-lg font-parisienne">~Gabor Maté</span>
            
            </article>

        </section>
        <div class="h-screen">

        </div>
</Layout>
